Revision history for JIP-Daemon

0.041   2018-01-07
        Updated Makefile.PL for version 2 of the CPAN distribution metadata specification.

0.04    2018-01-07
        Added devnull method.
        Added stdout method.
        Added stderr method.
        Added program_name attribute.
        Added change_program_name method.
        Increased JIP::ClassField version requirement to 0.05.
        Improved documentation.

0.03    2015-06-24
        Added on_fork_callback attribute.
        Sub::Util::set_subname() for all callback functions.
        Improved tests.

0.02    2015-06-20
        Renamed detached attribute to is_detached.
        Fixed parameter order for POSIX::kill.
        Improved tests.
        More reference docs.

0.01    2015-06-12
        First version, released on an unsuspecting world.
